subSection.paragraph:
All sequences were aligned in Clustal W (
Thompson et al. 1994
) by default parameters, and posteriorly reviewed by eye in order to check for frameshifts, indels or stop codons in MEGA 5 (
Tamura et al. 2011
); the matrix was completed with ambiguous state characters (i.e., n). Genetic divergence was determined by calculating p-distances ( MEGA 5,
Tamura et al. 2011
). Substitution model GTR+I+gamma was selected with jModelTest ( Posada 2008 ), by AIC (using the “propose model” routine). In order to recover phylogenetic relationships, we analyzed the sequence matrix by Maximum Likelihood (ML) and Bayesian inference (BI). ML analysis was conducted using the Randomized Accelerated Maximum Likelihood (RAxML) algorithm version 7.0.4 ( Stamatakis 2006 ) with 10,000 bootstrap pseudo-replicates to search for the best tree and bootstrap support (BS). BI analysis was performed with MrBayes 3.2.6 ( Ronquist & Huelsenbeck 2003 ); four simultaneous Markov chains were run for 20,000,000 generations, with a sampling frequency of 1,000 generations. Convergence on a stable loglikelihood value was verified by plotting the log-likelihood values against generation time for each chain. The first 25% of the trees were discarded as burn-in and the remaining trees were used to compute a 50% majority rule consensus tree and to obtain posterior probability (PP) estimates for each clade.

subSubSection.paragraph:
Etymology. Dedicated in tribute to Mario Vargas Llosa, Peruvian writer and Nobel Prize winner in Literature 2011. Mario Vargas Llosa was born in Arequipa , Peru as N.H., and lived in Bolivia (as the current range of
N. vargasllosai
) the first years of his childhood until he returned back to Peru . He studied Laws in the Universidad Nacional Mayor de San Marcos, alma mater of V.P. and N.H.

